#--- GeoTag Add New Tag ---

### geotag add: all params
POST http://localhost:3000/api/geotags HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"Test", 
    "lat":"49.01379",
    "long":"8.404435",
    "tag":"#test"
}

### geotag add: no params
POST http://localhost:3000/api/geotags HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json


#--- get GeoTag ---

### get GeoTag with ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/0 HTTP/1.1

### get GeoTag wrong ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/-1 HTTP/1.1


#--- update GeoTag ---

### update GeoTag: all params
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/0 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"Test - Castle", 
    "lat":"49.01379",
    "long":"8.404435",
    "tag":"#test"
}

### update GeoTag: wrong id
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/-1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"Test - Castle","lat":"49.01379","long":"8.404435","tag":"#test"}

### update GeoTag: no params
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/0 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### update GeoTag: missing params
