### delete GeoTag
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/0 HTTP/1.1

### delete GeoTag: wrong id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/-1 HTTP/1.1


#--- GeoTag Backend Demonstrator ---
#Backend Demonstrator mit generischem HTTP-Client
#Lebenszyklus für GeoTag vorführen: Erstellen, Auslesen, Ändern, Suchen, Löschen

### Erstellen
POST http://localhost:3000/api/geotags HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"Demo GeoTag", 
    "lat":"10",
    "long":"10",
    "tag":"#demo"
}

### Auslesen
GET http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/11 HTTP/1.1

### Ändern
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/11 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"Demo GeoTag Changed", 
    "lat":"50",
    "long":"50",
    "tag":"#demoChanged"
}

### Suche
GET http://localhost:3000/api/geotags?search=Demo&lat=50&long=50 HTTP/1.1

### Löschen
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/geotags/11 HTTP/1.1